He said something.

330
00:19:26,471 --> 00:19:29,012
他说  "你来这里是有原因的"
He said, "You're here for a reason."

331
00:19:29,416 --> 00:19:32,268
-不过不是说我  他是指沃克  -茱尔斯
- Only not me, he said Walker. - Jules?

332
