I know Peter, he's still up there.

347
00:20:26,723 --> 00:20:28,393
你如何肯定
What makes you so sure.

348
00:20:28,806 --> 00:20:31,166
小时候为了躲避喝醉了酒
He used to hide in the attic when we were kids,

349
00:20:31,665 --> 00:20:36,999
