No offence, but I don't think he's the one who's scared.

352
00:20:52,476 --> 00:20:55,524
你能往上看吗  我什么都看不到
Will you look up? I can't see anything.

353
00:20:57,075 --> 00:20:58,429
我这也是
Join the club. 

354
00:20:59,203 --> 00:21:00,204
那是什么
What was that?

355
00:21:00,802 --> 00:21:01,979
什么是什么
What was what?

356
00:21:06,207 --> 00:21:08,238
把你的头抬高二十度左右
Tilt your head up about 20 degrees.

357
00:21:08,784 --> 00:21:09,999
向左看
Now look left.

358
00:21:13,733 --> 00:21:15,708
这里黑得很  看到了吗
It's dark up here. Get it?

359
00:21:16,179 --> 00:21:18,366
检查正后方  确认他没跟在你后边
Check your six. Make sure he's not behind you.

360
