那电棍含有60万伏电压
That stun baton packs 600KV.

370
00:22:34,089 --> 00:22:35,241
他应该已经毫无知觉了
It should have knocked him out cold.

371
00:22:35,242 --> 00:22:36,101
看起来很多常理
Seems like a lot of things

372
00:22:36,102 --> 00:22:38,213
已经不能应用到彼得身上了
that should be happening with Peter aren't.

373
00:22:38,861 --> 00:22:39,910
基地一号
Base One.

374
