好的  我们马上去
Ok, we're on our way.

375
00:22:43,320 --> 00:22:44,949
楼上的升降机警报刚刚响了
Elevator alarm just went off upstairs.

376
00:22:44,950 --> 00:22:46,449
有人想要离开基地
Someone's trying to leave the base.

377
