纳尔维克-A组实验对象大量死亡
NARVIK-A subjects are decimated.

378
00:22:52,557 --> 00:22:54,802
接近百分之百的死亡率
Close to a 100% mortality rate.

379
00:22:55,078 --> 00:22:58,696
-纳尔维克-B呢  -百分之百出现病症
- And NARVIK-B? - Morbidity at 100%,

380
00:22:58,697 --> 00:23:00,370
可死亡率为零
mortality at zero.

381
00:23:00,597 --> 00:23:02,635
受了感染但是还活着
They're infected but still alive.

382
00:23:05,368 --> 00:23:08,883
我已经很久没在实验室干过活了
It's been a long time since I did real lab work.

383
00:23:09,003 --> 00:23:10,881
你一定已经忘了它能有多无聊吧
Guess you forget how tedious it can be.

384
00:23:10,882 --> 00:23:12,802
不是  我很怀念
No, I miss it.

385
00:23:13,324 --> 00:23:15,151
那些力求精准
The precision,

386
00:23:15,152 --> 00:23:17,386
全心投入  与不畏牺牲的精神
commitment, sacrifice,

387
00:23:17,387 --> 00:23:20,691
一切都是为了发现新事物的喜悦
all leading to the joy of discovery.

388
00:23:24,948 --> 00:23:27,471
我母亲以前也经常对我这么说
My mother used to say something just like that.

389
00:23:28,243 --> 00:23:30,922
她也是个科学家吗
She was also a scientist?

390
00:23:31,069 --> 00:23:33,451
细胞生物学家
Cellular biologist, yeah.

391
00:23:34,892 --> 00:23:36,734
她在我很小的时候就去世了
She died when I was very young.

392
00:23:37,459 --> 00:23:38,669
我很遗憾
I am sorry.

393
00:23:40,145 --> 00:23:41,687
你父亲呢
What about your father?

394
00:23:53,210 --> 00:23:54,246
天呐
Oh, my god.

395
00:24:08,722 --> 00:24:10,384
你能让他歇会吗
Can't you make him stop?

396
00:24:10,439 --> 00:24:12,878
吗啡不管用  如果我给他更大剂量
Morphine isn't working. If I give him any more,

397
00:24:12,879 --> 00:24:13,994
可能会致死
I might kill him. 

398
00:24:13,995 --> 00:24:15,448
是吗  那听起来也不错
Yeah, maybe that's not such a bad idea.

399
00:24:15,449 --> 00:24:16,303
有点同情心好吗
Nice. 

400
00:24:16,304 --> 00:24:17,379
要是换你躺在那儿
I suppose you'd feel the same way 

401
00:24:17,380 --> 00:24:18,308
看你还能不能说出这种话
if it was you lying there?

402
00:24:18,309 --> 00:24:20,501
我替海文感到难过  但这于事无补
Look, I feel sorry for Haven, but those are the breaks.

403
00:24:20,502 --> 00:24:22,412
能别吵了吗  我们要有耐心
Everybody, please. We just need to be patient.

404
00:24:22,413 --> 00:24:23,516
你说得倒轻巧
That's easy for you to say;

405
00:24:23,517 --> 00:24:24,662
你穿着防护服呢
you're back inside that suit.

406
00:24:24,663 --> 00:24:25,636
这只是我们研究出治疗方法
This is just a precaution

407
00:24:25,637 --> 00:24:26,972
之前的一种防护措施
until we figure out a treatment.

408
00:24:26,973 --> 00:24:28,849
你根本就没在想治疗方法
You're not figuring out a treatment.

409
00:24:28,850 --> 00:24:30,707
说实话  我觉得你对这种病毒
In fact, I don't think you know a damn thing 

410
00:24:30,708 --> 00:24:31,861
压根屁都不懂
about this virus at all.

411
00:24:31,862 --> 00:24:36,643
别吵了  我们都是博士  不是吗
Stop it! Stop. We're all doctors here, right?

412
00:24:39,493 --> 00:24:41,973
与其争吵  不如我们群策群力
Instead of bickering, let's put our heads together.

413
00:24:41,974 --> 00:24:45,073
没错  让她放我们出去
Yeah, let's get her to let us out of here.

414
00:24:45,074 --> 00:24:46,341
你知道我不能这么做
You know I can't do that.

415
00:24:46,342 --> 00:24:48,745
你可能会传染给别人或具有攻击性
There's a chance that you could infect others or become violent--

416
00:24:48,746 --> 00:24:51,194
如果这里的人变得有攻击性呢
And what if someone gets violent inside this box,

417
00:24:51,195 --> 00:24:52,667
那我们又该怎么办
What are we supposed to do then?

418
00:24:54,268 --> 00:24:55,154
把门打开
Open the door.

419
00:24:55,155 --> 00:24:57,812
至少让我们回自己的实验室
At least let us go back to our labs.

420
00:24:57,813 --> 00:24:58,819
不行
No.

421
00:25:04,386 --> 00:25:06,606
随你做什么  反正我是不会放你们走的
Do what you want, but I'm not letting you out of here.

422
00:25:06,832 --> 00:25:08,734
那就叫愿意放走我们的人来
Then you're gonna call someone who will.

423
00:25:12,586 --> 00:25:13,602
一号基地
Base One.

424
