A couple of detainees are demanding to be let loose.

426
00:25:21,094 --> 00:25:22,589
他们挟持了乔丹博士
They're holding Dr. Jordan.

427
00:25:24,058 --> 00:25:26,089
你去吧  我去检查外面
Go. I'll check outside,

428
00:25:26,160 --> 00:25:27,515
确保周边安全
secure the perimeter.

429
00:25:31,612 --> 00:25:34,317
各安保小队  请确认楼层已封锁
Security teams, confirm level lockdown.

430
00:25:36,039 --> 00:25:38,087
立即释放乔丹博士
Release Dr. Jordan at once.

431
00:25:38,088 --> 00:25:39,558
然后我们再谈
Then we can talk. 

432
00:25:39,702 --> 00:25:41,011
放我们出去  我们就放了她
Let us out and she comes with us.

433
00:25:41,012 --> 00:25:41,964
我保证不伤害她
No harm done.

434
00:25:41,965 --> 00:25:43,634
如果你让我们回实验室
If you let us back to our labs, 

435
00:25:43,635 --> 00:25:45,061
我们可以帮忙研究病毒
we can help with the virus.

436
00:25:45,062 --> 00:25:47,278
布赖斯是血液学家  我是生化学家
Bryce is a hematologist; I'm a biochemist.

437
00:25:47,279 --> 00:25:49,687
隔离是为了你们自身的安全
You are in isolation for your own safety.

438
