更像是被关在笼子里的老鼠
More like rats in a box.

439
00:25:50,908 --> 00:25:52,249
我们不会坐以待毙的
We're not gonna die in here.

440
00:25:52,250 --> 00:25:54,734
我们正在研究抗病毒疗法
We are working on an antiviral therapy.

441
00:25:54,735 --> 00:25:56,687
只要动物试验一开始
As soon as we run animal trials--

442
00:25:56,688 --> 00:25:58,444
