Animal trials could take weeks!

443
00:25:58,445 --> 00:26:01,906
我们可等不了那么久  你应该明白
We're not going to be around that long, and you know it.

444
00:26:06,927 --> 00:26:08,372
法拉格特博士
Dr. Farragut.

445
00:26:10,501 --> 00:26:12,577
放了乔丹博士
I need you to let Dr. Jordan go.

446
00:26:12,940 --> 00:26:14,308
想都别想  别过来
Uh-uh! Don't come any closer!

447
00:26:14,309 --> 00:26:16,826
听着  我们正竭尽全力
Look, we're working as hard as we can

448
00:26:16,868 --> 00:26:20,140
解决问题  不达目的不罢休
to figure this thing out, and we won't stop until we do.

449
00:26:20,141 --> 00:26:21,378
我们才不会信你的鬼话
We both know that's a crock of shit.

450
00:26:21,379 --> 00:26:22,616
先让他说完  布赖斯
Hear him out, Bryce.

451
00:26:22,617 --> 00:26:25,409
听我说  我和你们一样在里面
Listen, I'm in here with you;

452
00:26:25,410 --> 00:26:26,712
