454
00:26:28,923 --> 00:26:31,777
好吗  把注射器给我
All right? Just give me the syringe

455
00:26:31,829 --> 00:26:33,636
放开乔丹博士
and let Dr. Jordan go. 

456
00:26:33,636 --> 00:26:35,121
我们凭什么相信你
Why should we trust you?

457
00:26:48,499 --> 00:26:49,901
法拉格特博士
Dr. Farragut.

458
00:26:58,581 --> 00:27:00,303
现在我们没区别了
Now we're in this together.

459
00:27:13,111 --> 00:27:15,006
艾伦  刚才你所做的一切
Alan, what you did back there...

460
00:27:21,183 --> 00:27:22,232
