Thank you.

461
00:27:24,044 --> 00:27:25,672
我只是在尽我的职责
I was just doing my job.

462
00:27:26,200 --> 00:27:29,214
你不是也坚守岗位  没放他们出去吗
And so were you by not letting them leave.

463
00:27:29,300 --> 00:27:32,758
-严师出高徒  -是吗  哪个老师
- I had a good teacher. - Yeah? Do I know him?

