465
00:27:37,713 --> 00:27:39,846
它不通过空气传播
what with the lack of airborne transmission.

466
00:27:42,547 --> 00:27:43,740
茱尔斯  什么事
Jules, what is it?

467
00:27:45,022 --> 00:27:46,425
我要给你看点东西
I need to show you something.

468
00:27:48,537 --> 00:27:50,826
纳尔维克-A的试验对象死状恐怖
The NARVIK-A subjects died horribly -

469
00:27:50,884 --> 00:27:52,860
